---
const components = [
  {
    title: 'Streaming ticker tape',
    description:
      'Request a dataline to stream real-time price updates. Fast local queries with pre-aggregated bars - from 5 seconds to yearly resolutions. Extended hours and pre-market included.',
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13h2l3-8 4 16 3-8h6" /></svg>`,
  },
  {
    title: 'Direct broker access',
    description:
      'Bring your own broker. Your cash and assets stay in your name, at your broker — not held by an intermediary platform that can freeze withdrawals or collapse overnight. Direct connection gives you full control over execution and positions.',
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.5 21 3 16.5m0 0L7.5 12M3 16.5h13.5m0-13.5L21 7.5m0 0L16.5 12M21 7.5H7.5" /></svg>`,
  },
  {
    title: 'Signal data',
    description:
      'Instant local access to technical indicators, financial metrics and market trend signals. Vectorised computation for your entire universe of instruments. Need a custom indicator? Add it to the computation pipeline.',
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 6.375c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125S3.75 8.653 3.75 6.375m16.5 0c0-2.278-3.694-4.125-8.25-4.125S3.75 4.097 3.75 6.375m16.5 0v11.25c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125V6.375m16.5 0v3.75c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125v-3.75m16.5 3.75v3.75c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125v-3.75" /></svg>`,
  },
  {
    title: 'Risk engine',
    description:
      'Circuit breakers activate when conditions are met - drawdown limits, volatility thresholds or earnings proximity without P&L buffer. Parametrise your rules once and let the system hold the line.',
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 0 1 3.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 0 0 3 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285Z" /></svg>`,
  },
  {
    title: 'Trading agents orchestration',
    description:
      'Deploy trading agents, each running as an isolated client with its own capital allocation and internal state. All orders route through a central message bus to the shared risk engine and execution layer — ensuring max purchase amount and global exposure limits are enforced, regardless of how many agents are running.',
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 8V4H8" /><rect width="16" height="12" x="4" y="8" rx="2" /><path d="M2 14h2" /><path d="M20 14h2" /><path d="M15 13v2" /><path d="M9 13v2" /></svg>`,
  },
  {
    title: 'Smart triggers',
    description:
      'Set up a comprehensive trade plan by chaining entry, add, reduce, and exit using smart triggers. Glasshouse watches the conditions and submits orders only when they are met — keeping your levels hidden from the book until execution.',
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m3.75 13.5 10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75Z" /></svg>`,
  },
];
---

<section id="architecture" class="px-6 py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-text-primary sm:text-4xl">
      What's behind the glass
    </h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-center text-text-secondary">
        Glasshouse is the headless infrastructure that gives you full, end-to-end control over your investments — the plumbing that turns a decision into a live position. Signal scanning, position sizing, order execution, exposure monitoring: connected, persistent, and running whether you're at your desk or not.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
      {components.map((component) => (
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-accent/10 bg-bg-elevated p-8 transition-colors hover:border-accent/30">
          <h3 class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-xl font-semibold text-accent">
            <Fragment set:html={component.icon} />
            {component.title}
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">{component.description}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
